      },
      "date": "2014-05-13 15:56:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\nEven if we wanted to return liblustre in the future, it would make sense to handle the <liblustre.h> definitions via headers in libcfs/include/libcfs/posix/.  The liblustre.h header predates the separation of headers with architecture-specific sub-includes, so that would be a better way to go.",
